title: BRIEF-Bacanora ‍Intends To Re-Commence Process Of Changing Domicile Of Jurisdiction From Canada To Uk​
text:
February 9, 2018 / 7:31 AM / in 10 minutes BRIEF-Bacanora ‍Intends To Re-Commence Process Of Changing Domicile Of Jurisdiction From Canada To Uk​ Reuters Staff 1 Min Read 
Feb 9 (Reuters) - Bacanora Minerals Ltd: 
* INTENDS TO RE-COMMENCE PROCESS OF CHANGING DOMICILE OF JURISDICTION FROM CANADA TO UK​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Bangalore.newsroom@thomsonreuters.com)
